dolfin-adjoint
--------------

This repository provides the source code for dolfin-adjoint, see www.dolfin-adjoint.org

Installation:
-------------

See separate file INSTALL for how to install the module and a list
of dependencies. If you're on Ubuntu, just do

    sudo apt-add-repository ppa:libadjoint/ppa
    sudo apt-get update
    sudo apt-get install python-libadjoint

to install dolfin-adjoint.

Documentation:
---------------

See dolfin-adjoint.org/documentation

License:
--------

The dolfin-adjoint software is freely available under the GNU LGPL, version 3.

